Help me figure a way out.

4
00:00:27,199 --> 00:00:29,559
Ning Sui told me again
to go to her home for dinner.

5
00:00:30,039 --> 00:00:31,440
(How about)

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:32,200
(I go with you?)

7
00:00:33,479 --> 00:00:34,799
We haven't seen each other
for a long time, Fei.

8
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:35,679
(Mr. Gu.)

9
00:00:35,719 --> 00:00:37,240
Do you want to grab dinner sometime?

10
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,759
I've got a new batch of wine.

11
00:00:39,159 --> 00:00:39,600
(Sounds great.)

12
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,399
Men are really unreliable.

13
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:42,679
Not now.

14
00:00:43,039 --> 00:00:44,560
Even thinking about it

15
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,799
makes me feel scared now.

16
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,079
(What about Ning Sui?)

17
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,479
(Even with her around?)

18
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:51,840
I don't know.

19
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,200
(Well.)

20
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,280
(I'll think of a way for you.)

21
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,840
What are those?

22
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,000
Why did you put my cousin's face on it?

23
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,920
I'm going to your home with you,

24
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,079
so I'm trying to get used to it first.

25
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,760
Just having a meal
and you have to rehearse?

26
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,959
It shows how much I value you.

27
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,319
Gu Shen.

28
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,480
Are you afraid of accompanying me home?

29
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,359
A little bit.

30
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,640
Take it easy.

31
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,640
I'm here.

32
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,760
You just need to enjoy your meal

33
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,280
and think of yourself as a mascot.

34
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,319
(How many people
are there in your family?)

35
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,599
(Where do you work?)

36
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,599
(How old are you?)

37
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,920
(What do your parents do?)

38
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,079
(Come on. Cheers.)

39
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:41,920
(Cheers.)

40
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,920
(Come on, boy. Don't be shy.)

41
