Gu Shen.

43
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:47,799
Gu Shen.

44
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:52,840
Ning Sui.

45
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,599
Thank you.

46
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,159
Why?

47
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,120
You're weird.

48
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,120
Have your breakfast.

49
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,560
I gotta go to the company early today.

50
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:07,560
Ji Chuan.

51
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:10,080
I think it's time
to tell Ning Sui about it.

52
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:14,000
The doll treatment really works?

53
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,080
It's not that.

54
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,599
It's because I feel safe

55
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:18,479
when she's around.

56
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,199
Good news, anyway.

57
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,639
I don't need to be
on call day and night.

58
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,039
What did you say?

59
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,680
I mean,

60
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,560
you should go out with her more often

61
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,319
to adapt to different environments.

62
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,840
It is helpful to you.

63
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:32,919
Okay?

64
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,639
I haven't come out
for a walk for a long time.

65
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,560
Yeah.

66
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,319
Me neither.

67
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,360
You're so careless.

68
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,800
Let me hold your hand.

69
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,479
Your mother

70
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,919
has got eyes around here too?

71
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,479
Yeah.


